data.description: Two homes for the price of one!! This full acre in Linden is complete with a 3 bedroom 2 bath home on the ground level and a large media/playroom room downstairs and an upstairs loft that can be used as an additional bedroom or office. All 3 levels have their own covered decks to enjoy the amazing views out the back that can also be enclosed for those chilly nights to enjoy watching the snowfall. The guesthouse is a 1 bedroom 1 bath cabin complete with full kitchen, laundry and living room with endless possibilities. You could have a guest home for family or even rent as a VRBO. Bonus is both homes do run on solar so no large bills in the summer or winter. Come and check it out today!
